Enum ExchangeStatus

    public enum ExchangeStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<ExchangeStatus>
    Enumeration of status codes returned by the SoaAgent.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CHALLENGE
      Indicates an authentication challenge is being issued.
      CONTINUE
      Indicates message processing completed successfully and normal flow should continue.
      RETURN_FAULT
      Indicates a fault message should be returned to the client immediately.
      RETURN_SUCCESS
      Indicates a successful message should be returned to the client immediately.
      TERMINATE
      Indicates the message processing should stop immediately and no response should be issued to the client.
